title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Claim the Dinka Blista Kanjo, Plus Get the Dinka Tee
content:
Infiltrate The Diamond Casino & Resort for an opportunity to claim your robbery target: the Dinka Blista Kanjo (Compact), styled with an LS Pounders license plate. Check the computer in your Salvage Yard to start planning The Podium Robbery.

Plus, get your hands on the Dinka Tee for free by purchasing any of the following triad of discounted sports cars — the Dinka Jester RR (Sports), Dinka RT3000 (Sports), or Dinka Sugoi (Sports) — all available at a tempting 30% off.
